vote.title: Authorize a twenty-year development, operation, and maintenance agreement, with one five-year renewal option, with CityMark 3100 McKinnon SPE, LLC, a Delaware limited liability company for the development, operation, and maintenance of pedestrian sidewalks, bike racks, grading, and landscape improvements for the purposes of connecting to and providing access from an adjacent development to the Katy Trail located at 3100 McKinnon Street - Financing: No cost consideration to the City
